title: Emacs Lisp , higher-order functions in
pid: ed824eee-35cd-4310-9a1c-311ef1f0dc7e
body: |2-
  (defun apply-to-one (func)
    (funcall func 1))

  ( message ( number-to-string
              ( apply-to-one ( lambda (arg)
                               ( + 1 arg ) ) ) ) )
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
